sentences.english: There is all this fresh stuff pouring through you.

sentences.english: There was no significant difference between female and male antennal sensilla.

sentences.english: The poison secreted by the gallfly produces monstrous growth on the wild rose or oaktree.

sentences.english: It moist, nourishes, renews and replenishes our skin cells, makes our skins beccoming more delicates and soft.

sentences.chinese: 研究了用萝卜苗作桃蚜寄主植物繁殖烟蚜茧蜂的技术。

sentences.english: Shawn was stung by the bee and his face is swollen.
The purring of the freezer had been the sea.
